---

<BaseLayout
  title="Forex Trading Basics: Complete Beginner's Guide 2026"
  description="Learn forex trading from scratch. Understand currency pairs, pips, leverage, and how to start trading forex in 2026. Free comprehensive guide for beginners."
>
  <!-- BREADCRUMB -->
  <Breadcrumb slot="breadcrumb" items={[
    { text: 'Home', href: '/' },
    { text: 'Guides', href: '/guides/' },
    { text: 'Forex Trading Basics', current: true }
  ]} />

  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-badge">
          <span class="badge-icon">üí±</span>
          BEGINNER'S GUIDE
        </div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Forex Trading Basics</h1>
        <p class="hero-description">
          Everything you need to know to start trading currencies. From understanding pips to choosing your first broker.
        </p>

        <!-- Key Stats -->
        <div class="stats-grid">
          {keyStats.map((stat) => (
            <div class="stat-card">
              <div class="stat-icon">{stat.icon}</div>
              <span class="stat-value">{stat.value}</span>
              <span class="stat-label">{stat.label}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ANCHOR NAVIGATION -->
  <nav class="anchor-nav" id="anchorNav">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="anchor-links">
        {anchorMenuItems.map((item) => (
          <a href={item.href} class="anchor-link">{item.text}</a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- WHAT IS FOREX -->
  <section class="section" id="what-is-forex">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">What is Forex Trading?</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Forex (FX) is the global marketplace for exchanging national currencies. It's the largest financial market in the world, with $7.5 trillion traded daily.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="intro-content">
        <p>When you travel abroad and exchange dollars for euros, you're participating in forex. When you trade forex online, you're speculating on whether one currency will strengthen or weaken against another.</p>
        <p>If you think the Euro will rise against the US Dollar, you buy EUR/USD. If you're right and the Euro strengthens, you sell for a profit. If you're wrong, you take a loss.</p>
      </div>

      <h3 class="subsection-title">Key Terms You Need to Know</h3>
      <div class="terms-grid">
        {forexBasics.map((item) => (
          <div class="term-card">
            <h4 class="term-name">{item.term}</h4>
            <p class="term-definition">{item.definition}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CURRENCY PAIRS -->
  <section class="section section-alt" id="pairs">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Major Currency Pairs</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Major pairs include the US Dollar and are the most traded. They have the tightest spreads and highest liquidity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pairs-table-wrapper">
        <table class="pairs-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Pair</th>
              <th>Name</th>
              <th>Nickname</th>
              <th>Typical Spread</th>
              <th>Volume</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {majorPairs.map((pair) => (
              <tr>
                <td class="pair-code">{pair.pair}</td>
                <td>{pair.name}</td>
                <td class="pair-nickname">{pair.nickname}</td>
                <td>{pair.spread}</td>
                <td>{pair.volume}</td>
              </tr>
            ))}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="pair-types">
        <div class="pair-type-card">
          <h4>Minor Pairs</h4>
          <p>Currency pairs without USD but with major currencies. Examples: EUR/GBP, EUR/JPY, GBP/JPY. Wider spreads than majors.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pair-type-card">
          <h4>Exotic Pairs</h4>
          <p>Major currency paired with an emerging market currency. Examples: USD/TRY, EUR/ZAR. Widest spreads, higher volatility.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TRADING SESSIONS -->
  <section class="section" id="sessions">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Forex Trading Sessions</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Forex markets are open 24 hours, 5 days a week. Different sessions have different characteristics.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="sessions-grid">
        {tradingSessions.map((session) => (
          <div class="session-card">
            <h3 class="session-name">{session.name}</h3>
            <p class="session-hours">{session.hours}</p>
            <p class="session-description">{session.description}</p>
            <div class="session-pairs">
              <strong>Best pairs:</strong> {session.bestPairs.join(', ')}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="session-tip">
        <p><strong>Pro tip:</strong> The London-New York overlap (8 AM - 12 PM ET) is the most active period with the highest volatility and tightest spreads.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT MOVES FOREX -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">What Moves Currency Prices?</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Understanding these factors helps you anticipate market movements.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="movers-grid">
        {marketMovers.map((mover) => (
          <div class="mover-card">
            <span class="mover-icon">{mover.icon}</span>
            <h3 class="mover-title">{mover.title}</h3>
            <p class="mover-description">{mover.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GETTING STARTED -->
  <section class="section" id="get-started">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">How to Start Forex Trading</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Follow these steps to begin your forex trading journey the right way.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="steps-grid">
        {gettingStartedSteps.map((step) => (
          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">{step.number}</div>
            <h3 class="step-title">{step.title}</h3>
            <p class="step-description">{step.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="section-cta">
        <a href="/brokers" class="cta-button primary">
          Compare Forex Brokers
        </a>
        <p class="cta-subtitle">
          Find a regulated broker with tight spreads
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ANALYSIS TYPES -->
  <section class="section section-alt" id="analysis">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Types of Forex Analysis</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Successful traders use one or more of these approaches to make trading decisions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="analysis-grid">
        {analysisTypes.map((type) => (
          <div class="analysis-card">
            <span class="analysis-icon">{type.icon}</span>
            <h3 class="analysis-title">{type.title}</h3>
            <p class="analysis-description">{type.description}</p>
            <p class="analysis-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> {type.bestFor}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COMMON MISTAKES -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Common Beginner Mistakes</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Avoid these pitfalls that trap most new forex traders.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mistakes-grid">
        {beginnerMistakes.map((item) => (
          <div class="mistake-card">
            <h3 class="mistake-title">{item.mistake}</h3>
            <p class="mistake-description">{item.description}</p>
            <p class="mistake-solution"><strong>Solution:</strong> {item.solution}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BROKERS SECTION -->
  <section class="section section-alt" id="brokers">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Best Forex Brokers for Beginners</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Regulated brokers with beginner-friendly platforms and educational resources.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="brokers-grid">
        {featuredBrokers.map((broker) => (
          <div class={`broker-card ${broker.featured ? 'featured' : ''}`}>
            {broker.featured && <span class="featured-badge">Top Pick</span>}
            <div class="broker-header">
              <img src={broker.logo} alt={`${broker.name} logo`} class="broker-logo" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="broker-rating">
                <span class="rating-stars">{'‚òÖ'.repeat(parseInt(broker.stars))}</span>
                <span class="rating-value">{broker.rating}/5</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="broker-name">{broker.name}</h3>
            <ul class="broker-features">
              {broker.features.map((feature) => (
                <li>{feature}</li>
              ))}
            </ul>
            <a href={broker.ctaLink} class="broker-cta">{broker.ctaText}</a>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="section-cta">
        <a href="/brokers" class="cta-button secondary">
          View All Forex Brokers
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ SECTION -->
  <section class="section" id="faqs">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Forex Trading FAQs</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Answers to the most common questions from forex beginners.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-list">
        {faqs.map((faq) => (
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary class="faq-question">{faq.question}</summary>
            <p class="faq-answer">{faq.answer}</p>
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="final-cta">
        <h2>Ready to Start Trading Forex?</h2>
        <p>Open a demo account to practice risk-free. When you're confident, start live trading with a regulated broker.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/brokers" class="cta-button primary">Find a Broker</a>
          <a href="/guides/day-trading" class="cta-button secondary">Learn Day Trading</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

